1
0:00:00:00.0000000 --> 0:00:00:00.0000000
At what planet did you steal your first spaceship?

2
0:00:00:00.0000000 --> 0:00:00:00.0000000
Spaceship?

3
0:00:00:00.0000000 --> 0:00:00:00.0000000
What is this spaceship that you speak of?

4
0:00:00:00.0000000 --> 0:00:00:00.0000000
Seriously, what happens to these spaceships?

5
0:00:00:00.0000000 --> 0:00:00:00.0000000
On which planet...

6
0:00:00:00.0000000 --> 0:00:00:00.0000000
…did you have your virgin space battle?

7
0:00:00:00.0000000 --> 0:00:00:00.0000000
The first alien I ever encountered….

8
0:00:00:00.0000000 --> 0:00:00:00.0000000
was the one who ate my entire stash of space food.

9
0:00:00:00.0000000 --> 0:00:00:00.0000000
Then I had another encounter, but I lost her after throwing away her space treasure map.

10
0:00:00:00.0000000 --> 0:00:00:00.0000000
And I won’t say more because the alien I almost captured, I lost her too.

11
0:00:00:00.0000000 --> 0:00:00:00.0000000
And the alien I brought on board,

12
0:00:00:00.0000000 --> 0:00:00:00.0000000
the one who ate my whole supply of space rations,

13
0:00:00:00.0000000 --> 0:00:00:00.0000000
she wouldn’t let me negotiate any terms.

14
0:00:00:00.0000000 --> 0:00:00:00.0000000
But she took all my fuel, the sneaky little cosmic thief.

15
0:00:00:00.0000000 --> 0:00:00:00.0000000
And I saw her laser gun because she dropped it—she had a malfunction, a big energy drain.

16
0:00:00:00.0000000 --> 0:00:00:00.0000000
And her robotic friend also raided my ship for supplies.
17
0:00:00:00.0000000 --> 0:00:00:00.0000000
Why didn’t you join the Galactic Empire?

18
0:00:00:00.0000000 --> 0:00:00:00.0000000
No way, I’m better off as a rogue pirate.

19
0:00:00:00.0000000 --> 0:00:00:00.0000000
Now that aliens see me in hyperspace, they all want to challenge me.

20
0:00:00:00.0000000 --> 0:00:00:00.0000000
I’m the captain of my own destiny, a lone space wolf.

21
0:00:00:00.0000000 --> 0:00:00:00.0000000
If I join the empire, they win and take all my loot.

22
0:00:00:00.0000000 --> 0:00:00:00.0000000
And because they watch holographic videos, they come running after me.

23
0:00:00:00.0000000 --> 0:00:00:00.0000000
There are space battles at sunrise, noon, sunset, and even during black holes.

24
0:00:00:00.0000000 --> 0:00:00:00.0000000
And when they get into asteroid fields, they leave.

25
0:00:00:00.0000000 --> 0:00:00:00.0000000
Do you think robots and humans can be friends?

26
0:00:00:00.0000000 --> 0:00:00:00.0000000
No, robots are programmed, humans have free will.

27
0:00:00:00.0000000 --> 0:00:00:00.0000000
I admire how clearly you explain astrophysics.

28
0:00:00:00.0000000 --> 0:00:00:00.0000000
It’s simple, isn't it?

29
0:00:00:00.0000000 --> 0:00:00:00.0000000
It’s rocket science!

30
0:00:00:00.0000000 --> 0:00:00:00.0000000
Did you hear there are now robot pirates?

31
0:00:00:00.0000000 --> 0:00:00:00.0000000
Yeah, I saw it in a space magazine. Now you can team up with them.

32
0:00:00:00.0000000 --> 0:00:00:00.0000000
Are you thinking of upgrading your ship's AI?
